  // Lowers a DSOL object literal to a stack-allocated bytes value
  // shaped like `{"key1":"<v1>","key2":"<v2>",...}`. The host syscall
  // handlers in `backend/dark-contracts/host.js` parse argv via
  // `JSON.parse`, so the wire format is JSON. Field encoding rules:
  //
