  //     using the new U64_TO_DEC_STR opcode. Quoted (not raw JSON
  //     number) so amounts > 2^53 don't lose precision through any
  //     hypothetical `Number()` round-trip in the host. The host's
  //     `String(argv.amount || '0')` + `BigInt()` handles both
  //     quoted and unquoted forms transparently.
